gw.api.profiler

Class FindGroupedQueriesByQueryTimeAnalyzer

  • gw.api.profiler.FindTopItemsAnalyzer<T,S>
    • gw.api.profiler.FindGroupedQueriesByQueryTimeAnalyzer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject

    public class FindGroupedQueriesByQueryTimeAnalyzer
extends FindTopItemsAnalyzer<T,S>
implements _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    Find the top n frames ordered by time to execute query (longest first). If n is not specified, all frames are returned. n can be specified as a percentage of total number of frames If given a SQL string, this will restrict the search to query frames containing that String.
